{"tid":772827,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山寨文化唔係中國獨享，韓國漫畫涉抄襲男兒當入樽","createTime":"2018-08-09T05:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T06:40:06.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e1ed2e96234f305b27f81f095f21cbec039386bb","tid":772827,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/09/132335_83de0d8c4d7ddbff519e6e3703d2f79d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2F132335_83de0d8c4d7ddbff519e6e3703d2f79d.png&h=f7d9951f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文化，很多人也許馬上想到中國，其實這方面，韓國亦不時受到指責。據日本媒體報道，韓國漫畫家金城模（김성모）的新作《高校生活記錄簿》，早前便飽受批評，不少漫畫迷都指他抄襲井上雄彥的《男兒當入樽》(SLAM DUNK)，最終金城模新作需下架腰斬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n漫畫家自稱練習臨摹過 30 冊單行本，因此畫風受井上雄彥影響。<br />\n【旅遊筍料】馬車都有 Uber？40 港元享受復古代步<br />\n<br />\n【網絡熱話】港鐵主席馬時亨開記召向公眾道歉！強調「有責任感」兩次請辭獲挽留<br />\n<br />\n《男兒當入樽》這本名作不但紅遍港日，在韓國亦相當有名，所以當金城模畫出《高校生活記錄簿》這部作品時，不少人馬上發現，當中的人物造型、分鏡等，都非常相似，甚至能直接疊加，隨即惹來不少批評。《高校生活記錄簿》本來在網上平台「Naver Webtoon」上載，但由於涉嫌抄襲，最終只連載了 4 話，便要腰斬下架。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「還原度」太高了吧？<br />\n金城模在 facebook 解釋，自己是《男兒當入樽》的粉絲，以前練習臨摹過 30 冊單行本，因此畫風受井上雄彥影響，並成為習慣。他表示已明白不能臨摹其他作者的漫畫，以後不會再犯下這種錯誤，並為事件致歉。<br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"http://piconyan.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpiconyan.net&d=YAiwTaAOMRcLGJI5bW5UrmowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=81a19f13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">piconyan.net</a>"},{"pid":"d60ae07e9ffc0ca9d6909d182ec1f4ba326a1efe","tid":772827,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b3d807144a550e8dad0535465118631209a55c","tid":772827,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161384f6f7baa8d43c6c8481deff11962d12daf9","tid":772827,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T06:11:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89ee715a607cfc35d8eaaa9390c198a9e185e5a","tid":772827,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T06:14:22.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"ccd2d2a7048a2ed125f13065ff8fd8cdb9aee10a","tid":772827,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T06:18:50.000Z","msg":"支畜同泡畜同種，有乜咁出奇"},{"pid":"3b4756372f8a33adca0a1606420db608d47c98ff","tid":772827,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T06:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}